\c 3
\s Ukwakhiwa kwelathi lokunikelwa kweminikelo
\p
\v 1 Isifikile inyanga yesikhombisa, labantwana bakoIsrayeli sebesemizini, abantu babuthana njengamuntu munye eJerusalema\x + Neh. 7.73.\x*.
\v 2 Kwasekusukuma uJeshuwa indodana kaJozadaki labafowabo abapristi, loZerubhabheli indodana kaSalatiyeli labafowabo, bakha ilathi likaNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli ukuze banikele iminikelo yokutshiswa phezu kwalo, njengokubhaliweyo emlayweni kaMozisi\x + Dute. 12.5,6.\x* umuntu kaNkulunkulu\x + Dute. 33.1.\x*.
\v 3 Basebemisa ilathi ezisekelweni zalo, ngoba ukwesaba kwakuphezu kwabo ngenxa yabantu belizwe, basebenikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni iminikelo yokutshiswa phezu kwalo, iminikelo yokutshiswa ekuseni lantambama\x + Nani 28.3,4.\x*.
\v 4 Basebesenza umkhosi wamadumba\x + 3.1. Neh. 8.14,17. Zek. 14.16.\x* njengokubhaliweyo\x + Eks. 23.16. Levi 23.34.\x*, \add banikela\add* iminikelo yokutshiswa insuku ngensuku ngenani, njengomkhuba, udaba losuku ngosuku lwalo\x + Nani 29.12-38.\x*.
\v 5 Langemva kwalokho umnikelo wokutshiswa njalonjalo\x + Eks. 29.38.\x*, lowekuthwaseni kwezinyanga\x + Nani 28.11.\x*, lowemikhosi yonke emisiweyo yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyayingcwelisiwe, lowakhe wonke owanikela ngesihle umnikelo wesihle eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Nani 29.39.\x*.
\v 6 Ngosuku lokuqala lwenyanga yesikhombisa baqalisa ukunikela iminikelo yokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, kodwa isisekelo sethempeli leN\nd kosi\nd* sasinga\add ka\add*bekwa\x + 3.1.\x*.
\v 7 Basebenika imali kubabazi bamatshe lakubabazi bezigodo, lokudla lokunathwayo lamafutha kumaSidoni lakumaTire\x + 1 Kho. 5.6,9. 2 Lan. 2.10.\x* ukuze balethe izigodo zemisedari zivela eLebhanoni bezisa elwandle eJopha\x + Josh. 19.46.\x*, ngokwemvumo kaKoresi inkosi yePerisiya kubo\x + 1.2,3. 4.3. 6.3.\x*.
\s Ukwakhiwa kwethempeli kuyaqaliswa
\p
\v 8 Langomnyaka wesibili wokufika kwabo endlini kaNkulunkulu eJerusalema, ngenyanga yesibili, baqalisa oZerubhabheli indodana kaSalatiyeli\x + 3.2. 2.2. 4.3.\x* loJeshuwa indodana kaJozadaki\x + 3.2. 2.2. 4.3.\x*, lensali yabafowabo, abapristi lamaLevi, labo bonke ababebuyile eJerusalema bevela ekuthunjweni; basebemisa amaLevi kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amabili kusiya phezulu\x + 1 Lan. 23.24.\x* ukongamela umsebenzi wendlu yeN\nd kosi\x + 1 Lan. 23.4.\x*\nd*.
\v 9 Kwasekusukuma oJeshuwa, amadodana akhe, labafowabo\x + 2.40.\x*, uKadimiyeli lamadodana akhe\x + 2.40.\x*, abantwana bakoJuda, njengo\add muntu\add* munye ukongamela abenzi bomsebenzi endlini kaNkulunkulu\x + 1 Lan. 23.4.\x*, amadodana kaHenadadi\x + Neh. 3.18,24. 10.9.\x*, amadodana abo labafowabo amaLevi.
\v 10 Abakhi sebebekile isisekelo sethempeli leN\nd kosi\nd*, bamisa abapristi begqokile\x + 2.69.\x* belezimpondo\x + 1 Lan. 15.24.\x*, lamaLevi, amadodana kaAsafi, elensimbi ezincencethayo, ukudumisa iN\nd kosi\x + 1 Lan. 15.16.\x*\nd*, njengokwezandla zikaDavida inkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 1 Lan. 6.31. 16.4,7. 25.1,2.\x*.
\v 11 Baphendulana ngokuhlabela bedumisa bebonga iN\nd kosi\x + 1 Sam. 18.7. Neh. 12.24.\x*\nd*, ngoba ilungile, ngoba umusa wayo \add umi\add* kuze kube nininini kuIsrayeli\x + 1 Lan. 16.34,41.\x*. Bonke abantu basebememeza ngokumemeza okukhulu ekuyidumiseni iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba isisekelo sendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* sasesibekiwe.
\v 12 Kodwa abanengi babapristi lamaLevi lenhloko zaboyise, abadala ababeyibonile indlu yokuqala, isisekelo salindlu sesibekiwe emehlweni abo, bakhala inyembezi ngelizwi elikhulu; kodwa abanengi baphakamisa ilizwi ngokumemeza ngentokozo\x + Hag. 2.3.\x*.
\v 13 Ngokunjalo abantu kabehlukanisanga umsindo wokumemeza kwentokozo lomsindo wokukhala kwabantu, ngoba abantu baklabalala ngokuklabalala okukhulu, umsindo waze wezwakala khatshana.
